Unsure if this is the intended behaviour: 
The autograder grades these wrong and correct although they have the same output
Correct:
select distinct track_title from track, writes where 'lyricist' = writes.role and track.track_id = writes.track_id;


Wrong:
select distinct track_title from track, writes where role = 'lyricist' and track.track_id = writes.track_id;
